room_title: Escape room "Pandemic" by America's Escape Game in Oxford (MS)
review: Had a really fun time! We did the Pandemic room and it was pretty challenging. There was not a lot of room for error, but our game master Blake was really awesome and helped us out. Definitely will come back!

room_title: Escape room "Pandemic" by America's Escape Game in Oxford (MS)
review: Had a wonderful time. Did the Pandemic scenario and is was really fun even with not finishing. Can't wait to try again. I recommend everyone go try it at least once. You'll be hooked after.
